</span></div>
        </li>
              <li>
          <div><div>  <a href="/blog/interviews/telling-complete-and-true-story-venezuela-conversation-alejandro-puyana-geoff" hreflang="en"><img loading="lazy" src="/sites/worldliteraturetoday.org/files/styles/medium_thumbnail/public/Puyana-anchor.jpg?itok=OA7EaIGO" width="250" height="175" alt="Alejandro Puyana with the cover to his book Freedom Is a Feast" typeof="foaf:Image" class="img-fluid image-style-medium-thumbnail" />

</a>

</div></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-richtitle"><p class="field-content"><a href="https://worldliteraturetoday.org/blog/interviews/telling-complete-and-true-story-venezuela-conversation-alejandro-puyana-geoff">Telling a Complete and True Story of Venezuela: A Conversation with…</a>
</p></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-author"><span class="views-label views-label-field-author field-name-field-blogauthor">By</span><span class="field-content field-name-field-blogauthor"><a href="/author/geoff-graser" hreflang="en">Geoff Graser</a>
</span></div>
